title: ISS Daily Summary Report – 1/20/2024
summary: Private Astronaut Mission (PAM) Axiom 3: SpaceX Crew Dragon Freedom successfully docked to the ISS at 4:56 AM CST today. With the arrival of the four private astronauts, Michael López-Alegría, Walter Villadei, Alper Gezeravcı, and Marcus Wandt, the ISS crew complement has increased to 11.
